Time":"2020-08-04T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"before the Hong Kong BN(O) Visa is available."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"屌你真係唔識字<br />\n佢係話有visa之前就唔該你地一家人一齊去以便處理<br />\n內文<br />\n<br />\nEntering the UK before the Hong Kong BN(O) Visa is available<br />\nIf you&rsquo;re not eligible to enter the UK under an existing immigration route, Border Force Officers may be able to consider granting &lsquo;Leave Outside the Rules&rsquo; at the UK border for a period of 6 months to you and your accompanying dependants.<br />\n<br />\nTo be considered, you&rsquo;ll need to show:<br />\n<br />\nyour identity<br />\nyour BN(O) citizen status<br />\nthat you normally live in Hong Kong<br />\nthat you can accommodate support yourself financially in the UK<br />\nYou&rsquo;ll also need to show evidence of any non-BN(O) dependants&rsquo; family links to you and you should travel together to the UK as a family unit. A dependant is any of the following:<br />\n<br />\nspouse or civil partner<br />\nunmarried partner<br />\nchild (under the age of 18 when they first applied)<br />\nother family members where they can show there is a high level of dependency"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"樓主唔pin呢個, 係鬼"},{"pid":"9117f602b73af2d90fe52c48408cea9b6e312eab","tid":2138843,"uid":9055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:46:37.000Z","msg":"唔識英文仲想移民去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90a0b69ecf90d05a80ca71e9a10ff9d614733ae","tid":2138843,"uid":31389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18809f01358777c6ee67dcd8059b54ed9ac04167","tid":2138843,"uid":198175,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"即係咁到明冇得玩太空人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;you should travel together to the UK as a family unit&quot;<br />\n如果要帶埋冇BNO嘅家屬過去申請BNO visa, 就要全家人一齊先過去英國<br />\n<br />\n非常懷疑Home